section.def:
GTC
                (地面運輸中心) means the ground transportation centre
            at the Airport;

PTB
                (客運大樓) means the passenger terminal building at
            the Airport;

paragraph.content:
the presence of an intruder or of an object that a person is, for reasons
                    of security, not permitted to bring onto the premises or place or any other
                    premises or place;

require any person to give his name and address and to produce any document
                    in his possession which is or contains evidence of his name and
                    address;

the licence is not displayed on an electronic device through an electronic
                    platform specified under section 110A(1)(c) of the Road Traffic
                    Ordinance (Cap. 374);

the licence cannot be read or scanned by the Authorized Person because of a
                    defect of the electronic device on which the licence is purportedly displayed;
                    or

for section 67(1) and (2), after the words “police officer”,
                        add “or an Authorized Person”. (13 of
                                2024 s. 73)

for the words “or a traffic warden in uniform”, there shall be
                        substituted the words “, a traffic warden in uniform or an Authorized Person
                        in uniform”;

all references in the Regulations to “the Commissioner”, not being
                            a reference to “the Commissioner of Police” or “the Government” shall be
                            substituted by references to “the Authority”;

subsection.content:
The Authority may charge a fee for the issue of a closed road
                                permit, such fee to be determined by the Authority with the approval
                                of the Commissioner.”;

paragraph.content:
for regulations 3(1) and (2), 8(1) and (3), 14(1) and (4),
                        30(1) and 40(1), after the words “The Commissioner”, there shall be added
                        “or, the Authority with the approval of the Commissioner,”;

for regulations 3(3) and 5(1), after the words
                        “The Commissioner of Police”, there shall be added “or the
                        Authority”;

for regulations 21(4) and 23(2), wherever after
                        the words “the Director”, there shall be added “and the
                        Authority”;
